OL,6,GChannel 4 will launch a new Christmas
OL,7,Gident this evening, marking the 40th
OL,8,Ganniversary of the channel and the
OL,9,Goriginal transmission of the film
OL,10,Gadaption of The Snowman.
OL,12,FThe 20-second sequence transports the
OL,13,FChannel 4 logo to a wintry setting
OL,14,Fwhere it oversees The Snowman, The
OL,15,FSnowdog and James, the boy from the
OL,16,Ffirst The Snowman film, playing in the
OL,17,Fsnow.
OL,19,FThis is the first time that all three
OL,20,Fcharacters will be seen on screen
OL,21,Ftogether.
OL,3,CChannel 4 marks 40th anniversary of The
OL,4,CSnowman with new ident
