OL,6,FThe ident will make its on air debut at
OL,7,F8pm tonight and will be shown regularly
OL,8,Fover the festive period.
OL,10,FThe ident was produced by award-winning
OL,11,Fproduction company Lupus Films (the
OL,12,Fproducers of The Snowman and The
OL,13,FSnowdog) and directed by Robin Shaw `
OL,14,Fin collaboration with Channel 4's
OL,15,Fin-house creative agency, 4Creative.
OL,3,CChannel 4 marks 40th anniversary of The
