OL,6,FThe animation has been produced in
OL,7,FLupus Films' trademark hand-drawn
OL,8,Fstyle, hand-crafted by Robin Shaw and a
OL,9,Fsmall team of animators using
OL,10,Ftraditional 2D techniques in animation
OL,11,Fprogramme TVPaint.
