SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1673184216
OL,6,F"The Snowman has been a part of
OL,7,FChristmas for four decades so what
OL,8,Fbetter way to mark the 40th birthday of
OL,9,Fboth Channel 4 and the animated
OL,10,Fadaptation of Raymond Briggs's beloved
OL,11,Fcharacter than with a set of hand
OL,12,Fcrafted idents featuring James and the
OL,13,FSnowman."It may or may not snow this
OL,14,Fmonth but it is guaranteed to be a
OL,15,Fwhite Christmas on Channel 4."
OL,3,CChannel 4 marks 40th anniversary of The
OL,4,CSnowman with new ident
