PN,35605
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F356A1673184216
OL,6,F"We are really honoured to have been
OL,7,Fasked to bring The Snowman back to life
OL,8,Ffor Channel 4 for the 40th anniversary
OL,9,Fof this very special animated Christmas
OL,10,Fclassic."It's particularly poignant for
OL,11,Fus at the time of the tenth anniversary
OL,12,Fof The Snowman and The Snowdog and
OL,13,Fafter the death earlier this year of
OL,14,Four long-time friend and collaborator,
OL,15,Fthe inimitable Raymond Briggs."
OL,17,FFor Channel 4 Creative:
